original_title: Angel, Alien and UFO Encounters from Another Dimension
overview: The universe is so complex that even the greatest scientific minds on earth ultimately acknowledge that we do not understand the forces and true nature of the cosmos, let alone our place within it. Now for the first time, we can see in this documentary the un-seeable and unbelievable has been caught on video by multiple individuals who have not only captured mind bending video of Entities, UFOs and Angels, but have been profoundly affected by their experiences.
tagline: Angel, Alien and UFO Encounters from Another Dimension
title: Angel, Alien and UFO Encounters from Another Dimension
